msgstr "`3`"

#: learn/04-the-tui-cockpit.md:122
msgid "**PR/MRs** — every open PR/MR across the fleet"
msgstr "**PR/MR** — toutes les PR/MR ouvertes à travers la flotte"

#: learn/04-the-tui-cockpit.md:122 CLI-DESIGN.md:121
