msgid "`haw-<version>-<target>.<ext>.sha256` — SHA-256 checksums"
msgstr "`haw-<version>-<target>.<ext>.sha256` — sommes de contrôle SHA-256"

#: DISTRIBUTION.md:21
msgid ""
"`haw-<version>-<target>.<ext>.sig` and `.pem` — cosign keyless signature + "
