"`Workspace::plan_sync` + `fan_out`)."

#: ARCHITECTURE.md:90
msgid ""
"**`DemoController`** (`hawser/src/main.rs:3052`) returns canned in-memory "
"data and reaches no workspace, git, or network. `haw dash --demo` renders "
"every view deterministically for GIF recordings and, crucially, for tests."
msgstr ""
